            "title": "港股升幅迅速擴大 重越兩萬六關",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">港股今早高開後升幅迅速擴大，開市不足20分鐘已重越兩萬六關。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20240318_FI_source-ap_港股.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20240318_FI_source-ap_港股.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">截至上午約9時56分，恒生指數報26001點，升321點或1.25%；稍早前最高曾見26035點。恒生科技指數暫也升1.44%，報4896點。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">中國平安(02318)暫是表現最佳藍籌，升約4.7%；理想汽車(02015)與昨天派首季成績表的比亞迪(01211)，股價暫也升超過4%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15936224-%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e5%8d%87%e5%b9%85%e8%bf%85%e9%80%9f%e6%93%b4%e5%a4%a7-%e9%87%8d%e8%b6%8a%e5%85%a9%e8%90%ac%e5%85%ad%e9%97%9c",
