        {
            "title": "華潤置地分拆REIT於深圳上市 涉兩內地購物商場 股價初段造好",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">華潤置地(01109)公布，擬將內地兩購物商場成立REIT在深圳上市；該股今早初段跑贏大市，升超過3%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">截至上午約9時39分，該股報32元，升3.43%；稍早前最高曾見32.14元，升3.75%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15936157-%e8%8f%af%e6%bd%a4%e7%bd%ae%e5%9c%b0%e5%88%86%e6%8b%86reit%e6%96%bc%e6%b7%b1%e5%9c%b3%e4%b8%8a%e5%b8%82-%e6%b6%89%e5%85%a9%e5%85%a7%e5%9c%b0%e8%b3%bc%e7%89%a9%e5%95%86%e5%a0%b4-%e8%82%a1%e5%83%b9",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/20240605_FI_source-web_01109-1.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-29 09:41:47",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "人行今進行259億元人幣逆回購操作 淨投放199億",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">人民銀行今日在公開市場進行259億元(人民幣‧下同)的7天期逆回購操作，操作利率1.40%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">計入今日有60億元逆回購到期，人行在公開市場淨投放199億元。</p>\n</div>",
