            "pub_date": "2026-04-29 09:34:25",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "滬指開市跌16點 深成指跌79點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">內地股市初段向下，上證綜指以4061點開市，跌16點或0.41%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">深證成指開市報14751點，亦跌79點或0.53%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滬深300指數跌20點或0.43%，開報4737點；創業板指數開市報3578點，跌18點或0.51%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15936115-%e6%bb%ac%e6%8c%87%e9%96%8b%e5%b8%82%e8%b7%8c16%e9%bb%9e-%e6%b7%b1%e6%88%90%e6%8c%87%e8%b7%8c79%e9%bb%9e",
